html:
544 U.S. 917

McTIZIC, AKA METIZIC
v.
UNITED STATES.

No. 04-8601.

Supreme Court of United States.

March 21, 2005.

1

C. A. 5th Cir. Reported below: 111 Fed. Appx. 255. Motions of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted, judgments vacated, and cases remanded for further consideration in light of United States v. Booker, 543 U. S. 220 (2005).
